Pemburu syaitan Mazhab Shilin
taat kepada ketua mereka.

321
00:21:48,520 --> 00:21:51,160
Kepada siapa komander menjawab?

322
00:21:51,240 --> 00:21:52,360
Dewa Naga.

323
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:57,440
Dewa Naga?

324
00:21:59,080 --> 00:22:00,120
