337
00:22:36,040 --> 00:22:37,400
Saya tidak fikir ia semudah itu.

338
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:39,320
Mari kita tunggu sedikit lagi.

339
00:22:41,280 --> 00:22:42,640
Kita perlu bertahan dahulu.

340
00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:48,520
Sekarang, saya perlu melawat suatu tempat dahulu.

341
00:22:50,480 --> 00:22:51,640
Pavilion Weimiao?

342
00:22:52,520 --> 00:22:53,560
Wangyan,

343
00:22:54,800 --> 00:22:56,400
apa rancangan awak?

344
00:22:57,840 --> 00:22:59,600
Adakah kita benar-benar hanya akan duduk di sini

345
00:23:01,520 --> 00:23:02,960
